{"tid":1176841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「學生動源」籲全體學生團結反送中  6月9日一同上街：港處危急存亡之秋","createTime":"2019-05-29T12:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T14:03:28.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30e8422865bbd5497f2541ad38f9e2f14f35c36b","tid":1176841,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"【引渡惡法】「學生動源」籲全體學生團結反送中：港處危急存亡之秋<br />\n<br />\n多間大專院校、中學的組織先後發起聯署反送中惡法，提倡港獨的學生組織「學生動源」亦發出「告全港學生書」，強調逃犯條例修訂草案審議在即，香港現今乃危急存亡之秋，<br />\n<br />\n而長久以來學生都是抗爭運動必不可少的力量，呼籲6月9日全體學生一同走上街頭，對抗惡法修訂，<br />\n<br />\n「日內學生動源會公佈反逃犯條例修訂入校計劃，屆時將公佈計劃詳情，歡迎全體學生加入有關計劃將反逃犯條例修訂意識帶入校園」。<br />\n<br />\n「學生動源」指出，近年學生力量在抗爭路上沉寂多時，但現時香港正處於危急存亡之秋，一旦條例修訂通過，勢必嚴重影響香港人生活環境，因此懇請全體中學生、<br />\n<br />\n大學生與他們團結一致反修例，保衞我城。<br />\n<br />\n「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林在其個人facebook指，希望聯絡發起中學組織聯署的人士，以便進行反修例入校計劃。他又表示，其母校佛教茂峰法師紀念中學的舊生，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主動找他參與該校的校友師生聯署聲明，令他很感動。<br />\n<br />\n鍾翰林表示，「學生動源」於6.9大遊行時，會在隊尾竪起組織旗幟作記認，「如非必要學生動源不會採取非常手段以作抗爭，但學生動源絕不會畏懼採取任何抗爭手段！希望全體學生屆時在加入學生動源隊伍！」<br />\n<br />\n鍾翰林早前於立會外參與反修例活動時，被指搶去1名示威者手持的旗桿上國旗，涉嫌刑事毀壞被捕，其後獲准保釋。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190529/59652883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190529%2F59652883&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=fb7be40f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190529%2F59652883&h=8ccdda4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190529/59652883</a>"},{"pid":"23eb86252613682f3d559c4b263e43cffdb171c7","tid":1176841,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024eb4f6b45fcfe35b5e704fbab96a02fc041380","tid":1176841,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49ebba4e1414d02323e8fdcb901d9b7a8225066","tid":1176841,"uid":5005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb3dc43d44795b0b8992e52915af09eb8187d3e","tid":1176841,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"除咗6月9號上街，希望大家都可以幫手聯署呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=5c6a2fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全球聯署、白宮聯署、學界、各行各業、宗教、地區/ 海外港人等等）反送中聯署合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY%2Fhtmlview&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=a905e3c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview</a>"},{"pid":"ebaaa4688e0443aa3ea8fbe5c6c04a89eb3c2c7f","tid":1176841,"uid":